The paper focuses on mobile edge computing, which involves the integration of mobile networks and cloud computing. This topic is closely related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also addresses the challenges of workload scheduling and resource allocation, which are common topics in systems and control (cs.SY) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper proposes an iterative algorithm based on Gibbs sampling and water filling, which involves optimization and information theory (cs.IT).
